hopobject.body: We need someone with experience shredded.sk Furthermore, don’t worry if you don’t click with people around you straight away. If you are struggling to find something in common why not use university or accommodation social media channels to reach a wider university audience in a fun and positive way. For example, start the conversation by trying to find someone from the same area as you, or tap into fan culture by searching for someone with a common passion for a favourite TV programme or band.
